modName: Eye of the Gods ENB - Natural Visuals for extreme low end systems
summary:
The guy who brought the Extreme Glow Vision ENB created a new fantastic ENB setup.
<br /><br />This is for people who LOVE a natural look. No oversaturated colors, blinding Bloom effects or strange lighting. All this ENB is focused on is providing a more natural look for minimal fps loss.
descriptionHtml:
What makes a good ENB?
There is no ENB that suits everyone, but here is my attemt to bring realistic visuals to low end systems, for a fps loss that is absolutely worth it! This ENB will enhance your gameplay experience by creating realistic lighting in EVERY single Dungeon, House, Palace and every environment inbetween.

Features:
-Enhanced realistic lighting based on vanilla data.
-Improved shadow contrast
-A decent Bloom that will soften your image.

-The smallest fps Impact possible with ENB.

Installation:
See Readme

Requirements:
- ENB binary files 0.102 Tatsudoshi
get it here: http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0102.htm


Highly recommended:
Dynavision by Gopher and MyGoodEye
for the awesome no-fps-loss depth of field effect you definately gonna enjoy, even without enb!

Use torches at night, its dark out there...
And use the mod "Lanterns on the Roads" by Svabbarjack
get this mod here: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10143/?
